Class MyBoundedGrid<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • MyBoundedGrid<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of object to be stored in the MyBoundedGrid.

    public class MyBoundedGrid<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    The MyBoundedGrid creates a grid capable of storing objects of type E. The grid is bounded and has a maximum number of rows and columns.
    Version:
    March 6 2019
    Author:
    Aditya Singhvi
